Title: Cancelled
Description: The contracting process was cancelled by the buyer or the procuring entity (for example, because of a change in needs, insufficient funds, or technical or procedural errors) after the contracting documents (for example, procurement documents) were available to potential supppliers, but not later than the bid submission deadline.

Title: Unsuccessful
Description: The contracting process failed (for example, no bids were received, all bids were withdrawn by the bidders, all bids were rejected by the buyer or the procuring entity) after the contracting documents (for example, procurement documents) were available to potential suppliers, but not later than the bid submission deadline.

Title: Withdrawn
Description: No further information on this process is available under this ocid.
